com.camerontec.util.datamodel.expression.compiler.tree

Interface ExpressionTreeVisitor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractExpressionTreeVisitor, DoNothingExpressionTreeVisitor, MultiplexingExpressionTreeVisitor

    public interface ExpressionTreeVisitor
    Classes implementing this interface are used to visit the nodes in an ExpressionTree.
